					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Briefly peeked at the source code.<br /><br />You should probably redo your graphics engine, since all pixels are being done with OpenGL draw calls to set the coordinates then set the color.<br /><br />The &quot;right&quot; way to do it is with a framebuffer and glTexSubImage2D.</div>

					
